VALLEY EARNINGS: PERFECTDATA CORP. PROFIT DOWN 84% IN 3RD QUARTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PerfectData Corp. reported net income of $4,000 for the fiscal third quarter 
that ended Dec. 31, down 84% from $25,000 in net income a year earlier. 
</P>
<P>
The Simi Valley company, which makes products for cleaning and maintaining 
computer equipment, said revenues declined 3% to $938,000 from $966,000. 
</P>
<P>
The company said the decline in earnings in the latest quarter reflected costs 
associated with launching a new line of devices that hold copy for computer 
users. 
</P>
<P>
For the nine months that ended Dec. 31, PerfectData reported $7,000 in 
earnings, compared to a loss of $24,000 in the year-earlier period. Revenues 
rose to $2.7 million from $2.6 million. 
</P>
