<HEADLINE>
<P>
NIBBLES AND BITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Kenneth Williams 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Supernumeraries, ballet's equivalent to television's extras, are being sought 
for American Ballet Theatre's "Romeo and Juliet" at the Orange County 
Performing Arts Center in March. 
</P>
<P>
ABT is seeking men from 5-feet-8 to 6-feet-2, women from 5-feet-6 to 5-feet-8, 
and boys, 9 to 12 years old, from 4-feet-6 to 4-feet-8. Auditions will be held 
Monday at the Center. Reservations must be made: (714) 556-2122, Ext. 558 for 
women and 557 for men and boys. 
</P>
