</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A group including Pacific Southwest Corp., a Northridge-based real estate and 
mortgage banking firm, acquired a 6% stake in Fairfield Communities Inc., a 
Little Rock, Ark., home builder, according to a filing with the Securities and 
Exchange Commission. 
</P>
<P>
