</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
COUSY, BOB; BASKETBALL HALL OF FAME; MANAGEMENT; RESIGNATIONS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA022790-0139 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 182244 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 27, 1990, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 9; Column 4; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
17 words 
</P>
